通信接口的皮肤电阻信号测量与分析系统","date":"2023-10-19T13:17:17.000Z","updated":"2023-10-19T13:32:58.071Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/文献阅读/基于USB通信接口的皮肤电阻信号测量与分析系统.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/covers/ReadPaper.png","text":"论文基本信息第一作者：汪后云 杨 圣 周 翔 谢明风 汪 琨 （中国科学技术大学工程科学学院，安徽 合肥 230031） 引用格式：[1]汪后云,杨圣,周翔等.基于USB通信接口的皮肤电阻信号测量与分析系统[J].工业控制计算机,2020,33(11):7-9. 链接： kns....","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":706,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"ReadPaper","slug":"ReadPaper","count":10,"path":"api/categories/ReadPaper.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"皮肤电阻","slug":"皮肤电阻","count":4,"path":"api/tags/皮肤电阻.json"},{"name":"时频分析","slug":"时频分析","count":2,"path":"api/tags/时频分析.json"},{"name":"数据采集","slug":"数据采集","count":1,"path":"api/tags/数据采集.json"},{"name":"USB","slug":"USB","count":1,"path":"api/tags/USB.json"},{"name":"音乐刺激","slug":"音乐刺激","count":1,"path":"api/tags/音乐刺激.json"}],"author":{"name":"KyrieYoung","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.postimg.cc/zfJznFjp/sakuragi.jpg","link":"/","description":"Sharping","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/40754875?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"}}}}}}